{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01E2efzdGNfgXnqZGHDw8pM3","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've found and read all the relevant files from the lord-of-rngs components directory. Here's a complete summary:\n\n## Files Found and Read\n\n### 1. **TierRoundView.tsx**\nMain component for displaying a specific tier's round. Features:\n- Back button to return to tier lobby\n- Phase indicator with countdown timer during countdown phase\n- Wheel visualization showing players or \"No players yet\" placeholder\n- Props: `tier`, `round`, `onBack`\n- Handles phases: waiting, countdown, spinning, revealing, complete\n\n### 2. **ActiveRoundView.tsx**\nComponent for displaying the currently active/joined round. Features:\n- Back to tiers button\n- Phase-dependent phase message\n- Countdown timer during countdown phase\n- Wheel visualization with current user tracking\n- Props: `round`, `currentUserAddress`, `onBackToTiers`\n- Different from TierRoundView in that it's for the round the user is actively in\n\n### 3. **TierLobby.tsx**\nThe main tier selection UI. Features:\n- Grid of 6 tier cards (iron, bronze, silver, gold, platinum, diamond)\n- Each card shows: tier gem icon, name, buy-in amount, player count, pool size, total entries\n- Shows phase label or countdown timer for each tier\n- Phase indicators with visual classes for different states\n- Handles loading state\n- Props: `tierStatuses`, `selectedTier`, `onSelectTier`, `loading`\n\n### 4. **WheelVisualization.tsx** (439 lines)\nComplex, high-performance wheel visualization component. Key features:\n- Horizontal scrolling wheel of player slots (infinite scroll illusion with 7x repetition)\n- Responsive slot sizing (6 slots @ 768px+, 5 @ 480px+, 4 below)\n- Player slots created based on entries (one slot per entry)\n- Placeholder empty slots for insufficient players\n- Animations:\n  - **Waiting/Countdown**: slow continuous scroll (40 px/sec)\n  - **Spinning**: 5-second spin with 3 full rotations + deceleration, lands on winner\n  - **Revealing/Complete**: stays locked on winner\n- Winner calculation using same logic as simulation\n- Virtualization during wait/countdown phases for performance\n- Winner announcement with star burst and coin animations\n- Legend showing all players sorted by odds with probability percentages\n- Props: `round`, `currentUserAddress`\n\n### 5. **CountdownTimer.tsx**\nSimple countdown timer component. Features:\n- Displays M:SS format\n- Two size variants: small, large\n- Optional \"until reveal\" label for large size\n- Visual urgency styles when ≤10 seconds remaining\n- Final countdown animation when ≤5 seconds\n- Props: `endsAt`, `size`, `onComplete`\n\n### 6. **index.ts**\nBarrel export file that exports all components:\n- `WheelVisualization`\n- `TierLobby`\n- `TierRoundView`\n- `ActiveRoundView`\n- `CountdownTimer`\n\n## Key Architecture Notes\n\n1. **Component hierarchy**: TierLobby → TierRoundView/ActiveRoundView → WheelVisualization\n2. **Wheel animation strategy**: Uses requestAnimationFrame with position-based scrolling (not CSS rotation)\n3. **Responsive design**: Adapts slot width and visible count based on window width\n4. **Performance**: WheelVisualization uses memoization, virtualization, and React.memo for sub-components\n5. **Phase-driven**: All components render differently based on round phase (waiting, countdown, spinning, revealing, complete)\n6. **Type imports**: Uses `Tier` from game-engine, `Round` from local types, and `TierStatus` for tier data\n\nAll files are complete and ready for reference."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a1e4a88 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 39888\ntool_uses: 9\nduration_ms: 15873</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2c77e434-3462-4e56-b7cd-45edfd147cc2","uuid":"84661cbc-2099-41c4-8473-e06f407dd25a","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Search for and read any file named TierRoundView or similar in the lord-of-rngs features directory:\n1. First glob for: /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/lord-of-rngs/**/*TierRound*\n2. Also glob for: /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/lord-of-rngs/**/*tier*\n3. Read any matching files completely.\n\nAlso check: /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/lord-of-rngs/components/ — list all files in this directory and read any that are related to displaying tier information or round views.\n\nReturn the complete contents of all relevant files.","agentId":"a1e4a88","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've found and read all the relevant files from the lord-of-rngs components directory. Here's a complete summary:\n\n## Files Found and Read\n\n### 1. **TierRoundView.tsx**\nMain component for displaying a specific tier's round. Features:\n- Back button to return to tier lobby\n- Phase indicator with countdown timer during countdown phase\n- Wheel visualization showing players or \"No players yet\" placeholder\n- Props: `tier`, `round`, `onBack`\n- Handles phases: waiting, countdown, spinning, revealing, complete\n\n### 2. **ActiveRoundView.tsx**\nComponent for displaying the currently active/joined round. Features:\n- Back to tiers button\n- Phase-dependent phase message\n- Countdown timer during countdown phase\n- Wheel visualization with current user tracking\n- Props: `round`, `currentUserAddress`, `onBackToTiers`\n- Different from TierRoundView in that it's for the round the user is actively in\n\n### 3. **TierLobby.tsx**\nThe main tier selection UI. Features:\n- Grid of 6 tier cards (iron, bronze, silver, gold, platinum, diamond)\n- Each card shows: tier gem icon, name, buy-in amount, player count, pool size, total entries\n- Shows phase label or countdown timer for each tier\n- Phase indicators with visual classes for different states\n- Handles loading state\n- Props: `tierStatuses`, `selectedTier`, `onSelectTier`, `loading`\n\n### 4. **WheelVisualization.tsx** (439 lines)\nComplex, high-performance wheel visualization component. Key features:\n- Horizontal scrolling wheel of player slots (infinite scroll illusion with 7x repetition)\n- Responsive slot sizing (6 slots @ 768px+, 5 @ 480px+, 4 below)\n- Player slots created based on entries (one slot per entry)\n- Placeholder empty slots for insufficient players\n- Animations:\n  - **Waiting/Countdown**: slow continuous scroll (40 px/sec)\n  - **Spinning**: 5-second spin with 3 full rotations + deceleration, lands on winner\n  - **Revealing/Complete**: stays locked on winner\n- Winner calculation using same logic as simulation\n- Virtualization during wait/countdown phases for performance\n- Winner announcement with star burst and coin animations\n- Legend showing all players sorted by odds with probability percentages\n- Props: `round`, `currentUserAddress`\n\n### 5. **CountdownTimer.tsx**\nSimple countdown timer component. Features:\n- Displays M:SS format\n- Two size variants: small, large\n- Optional \"until reveal\" label for large size\n- Visual urgency styles when ≤10 seconds remaining\n- Final countdown animation when ≤5 seconds\n- Props: `endsAt`, `size`, `onComplete`\n\n### 6. **index.ts**\nBarrel export file that exports all components:\n- `WheelVisualization`\n- `TierLobby`\n- `TierRoundView`\n- `ActiveRoundView`\n- `CountdownTimer`\n\n## Key Architecture Notes\n\n1. **Component hierarchy**: TierLobby → TierRoundView/ActiveRoundView → WheelVisualization\n2. **Wheel animation strategy**: Uses requestAnimationFrame with position-based scrolling (not CSS rotation)\n3. **Responsive design**: Adapts slot width and visible count based on window width\n4. **Performance**: WheelVisualization uses memoization, virtualization, and React.memo for sub-components\n5. **Phase-driven**: All components render differently based on round phase (waiting, countdown, spinning, revealing, complete)\n6. **Type imports**: Uses `Tier` from game-engine, `Round` from local types, and `TierStatus` for tier data\n\nAll files are complete and ready for reference."}],"totalDurationMs":15873,"totalTokens":39888,"totalToolUseCount":9,"usage":{"input_tokens":7,"cache_creation_input_tokens":14113,"cache_read_input_tokens":24864,"output_tokens":904,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":14113,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
